 Aminet is a large selection of Amiga files. Sites include:

  ftp.wustl.edu - pub/aminet
  doc.ic.ac.uk  - pub/aminet

 + many others. All have the same files on them and are regularly updated.

 If you are connected to the internet just @{"FTP" link "FTP" 0} to them, and type
 'cd /pub/aminet'. Then you can get all the files you want!
@endnode

@node "FTP" "FTP"
FTP is program for transfering files between one computer to another on the
internet. If you have access to a computer on the internet then chances are
you have access to FTP.
@endnode

